# =============================================================================
# stswasm .gitignore
#
# This repo ships source + the ikvmcraft artifacts we link against (vendor/).
# Proprietary game assets and the large external toolchains (Emscripten SDK,
# .NET wasm runtime pack) are excluded. See README.md.
# =============================================================================

# --- Proprietary game assets (NEVER commit) ----------------------------------
# Slay the Spire is copyrighted by Mega Crit. You must supply your own copy.
desktop-1.0.jar
**/desktop-*.jar
Slay.the.Spire*/
Slay.the.Spire*.zip
# Default local drop-in location for your own desktop-1.0.jar (build.sh STS_JAR).
/game/

# --- External toolchains (large; not committed) ------------------------------
# Install these or place/symlink them under vendor/ (or point EMSDK /
# DOTNET_WASM_PACK elsewhere). The Emscripten SDK exceeds GitHub's file limit.
/vendor/emsdk/
/vendor/dotnet/

# --- .NET / loader build output ----------------------------------------------
loader/bin/
loader/obj/

# --- Java launcher build output ----------------------------------------------
launcher/out/

# --- Native (Emscripten) build output ----------------------------------------
# NOTE: the prebuilt outputs native/libgdx.a, native/libgdxfreetype.a and the
# generated loader/statics.c ARE committed so `publish` works without re-running
# the heavy `native` target (which needs emsdk + the libGDX 1.9.5 source tree).
native/obj/
native/obj-freetype/
native/*.o

# --- Frontend deploy output (regenerated by `./build.sh deploy` / `sts-jar`) --
frontend/public/_framework/
frontend/public/image/
frontend/public/jars/

# --- Generated launcher jar (produced by `./build.sh launcher`) --------------
jars/stswasm-launcher.jar

# --- Misc build / OS / editor cruft ------------------------------------------
node_modules/
*.log
*.tmp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
